<i>adverb</i>: 소담스레 [소담스레] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>소담스레 [소담스레]</dt><br>
<dd>1. attractively</dd><br>
<dd>보기에 탐스럽게.</dd><br>
<dd>With an attractive look.</dd><br>
<dd>2. deliciously</dd><br>
<dd>음식이 매우 넉넉하여 먹음직하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Food looking abundant and delicious.</dd><br>
